    "description": "<p>Club HEAL (Hope, Empowerment, Acceptance &amp; Love) is a registered non-profit organization in Singapore that focuses on assisting and empowering individuals with mental health challenges. Our mission is to help them regain confidence in themselves and others as they reintegrate into the community. Club HEAL is an approved Institution of Public Character and a member of the National Council of Social Service (NCSS). We are also part of the Community Mental Health Intervention Teams (COMIT) and Community Resource Engagement and Support Team (CREST) programs under the Ministry of Health (MOH).</p>",
